attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes & Gardens - Wine Country Group
Better Homes & Gardens - Wine Country Group

data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home located in Spring Valley. This 3bd 2bth home has a ton of features including NEW laminate flooring throughout, NEW A/C only a year and a half old, NEW 30-year roof on the garage, and updated bathrooms! The kitchen has tons of cabinets for storage and a separate breakfast nook. The living room features a wood burning fireplace with plenty of room for the family to gather. The master bedroom has a private seating area, walk in closet, master bathroom with a soaking tub and separate shower. The laundry room is conveniently located within the home and includes an extra large soaking sink! With access from the garage to the laundry room, dirty clothes, and shoes, can be left aside without tracking dirt throughout the home.  The property is just under an acre and FULLY FENCED with a variety of mature trees. It also has several outbuildings for all your tools and toys. Located on a safe road and cul-de-sac, this property is perfect for the kids to run, farm animals, or extra elbow room from neighbors. With views of the valley and surrounding hills you're sure to love sitting on the front porch enjoying your new home!
